column2: "What am I doing? Observing. Not any one person, just everyone."
"It's really interesting. There are tons of people here and yet no two people are exactly the same."
"I guess that's to be expected. But I wonder why...."
"For some reason, in my head, everyone seemed to have the same face."
"I... can't remember. I know it doesn't do any good to get frustrated. I guess I'll relax."
"I'm still not very good at talking to people, but I like looking at their faces. It's a lot of fun."
"For some reason, it makes me happy. Not sure why, but it just does."
